## Method 2: WebSocket API (Advanced Automation)

Your game has a full **WebSocket-based remote control API** for advanced automation!

### Architecture

```
[Test Script] â†’ [WebSocket Server] â†’ [Browser/Game]
   (Node.js)        (Port 8765)         (Window)
                                           â†“
                              GameTestingInterface.js
                                           â†“
                              Game Systems (Ship, Navigation, etc.)
```

### Step 1: Enable Test Mode

The WebSocket API requires test mode for security. Add `?testMode=true` to the URL:

```
http://localhost:8080/index.html?testMode=true
```

Or enable via localStorage in the console:
```javascript
localStorage.setItem('testMode', 'true');
location.reload();
```

