All commands return this structure:

**Success:**
```json
{
  "id": "cmd-1",
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    // Command-specific result data
  },
  "error": null,
  "timestamp": 1699123456789,
  "executionTime": 12
}
```

**Error:**
```json
{
  "id": "cmd-1",
  "success": false,
  "data": null,
  "error": {
    "code": "MISSING_PARAMETER",
    "message": "Missing required parameter: value",
    "details": {}
  },
  "timestamp": 1699123456789
}
```

